0.8 the original recipe
chocolate cheesecake
20cm pan

recipe 1 :
260g chocolate
540g philadelphia
180g creme fraiche
13g poudred e cacao
1 tsp vanilla
200g sugar

recipe2 :
226g chocolate
720g philly
100g creme fraiche
25g poudre cacao
160g sugar
3 eggs

recipe 3 :
220g chocolate
450g philly
200g creme fraiche
100g creme liquide
25g poudre cacao
80g sugar
2 oeufs


- 100g Sucre en poudre 
- 25g poudre cacao
- 150g Crème liquide (35% MG)
- 220g chocolat 70%
- philadelphia 450g
- Crème fraiche épaisse et entière de normandy  (40%) : 200g
- 2 œufs entier
	3

	small bowl
		sucre en poudre + cacao
		creme liquide
		chocolat 70% fondu
	big bowl
		philly + creme fraiche
	add 1 to 2
	whisk 2 eggs in small zlafa
	add to 2
	
	
	30 minutes 180 statique (+ vapor)
	1h30 115 degrés
	1h four éteint
		

crust :
150g oreo (-4 cookies fillings)
35g beurre
	mix oreos by themselves, once you have a powder mix with melted butter in bowl
170C chaleur tournante
	12 minutes
	



ganache :
100g chocolat 76%
90ml creme liquide

melt chocolate slowly
heat creme sepratly to 40C
combine

